{
  "info": {
    "name": "Macetero (local)",
    "description": "Pruebas contra `npm run dev` en http://localhost:3000\n\n**Trustless deploy:** requiere en `.env` / `web/.env.local`: `TRUSTLESS_WORK_ENABLED=true`, `TRUSTLESS_WORK_API_KEY`, `TRUSTLESS_SIGNER_SECRET` (o `TRUSTLESS_WORK_OPERATOR_SECRET`) con la cuenta que firma. Los `roles.*` del JSON deben ser coherentes con esa cuenta (o la wallet Macetero por defecto).\n\n**Webhook Etherfuse:** si `ETHERFUSE_WEBHOOK_SECRET` está vacío, el servidor acepta sin firma. Si no, la colección calcula `x-signature` (HMAC-SHA256 hex del body) en el script de carpeta.\n\nImportar: File → Import → este archivo.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000" },
    { "key": "ETHERFUSE_WEBHOOK_SECRET", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Raíz",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET / (comprueba que el servidor responde)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Trustless",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST /api/trustless/deploy (single-release)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"engagementId\": \"postman-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"title\": \"Prueba Postman\",\n  \"description\": \"Escrow de prueba\",\n  \"amount\": 10,\n  \"platformFee\": 0,\n  \"roles\": {\n    \"approver\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\",\n    \"serviceProvider\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\",\n    \"platformAddress\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\",\n    \"releaseSigner\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\",\n    \"disputeResolver\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\",\n    \"receiver\": \"GAMAANR75JRJX3GH7C7KOAIQC342HQQOFDOG7BCDB7MZXVB2IJMNWSZ3\"\n  },\n  \"milestones\": [\n    { \"description\": \"Primer hito\" }\n  ]\n}\n"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/trustless/deploy"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Etherfuse webhook",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('ETHERFUSE_WEBHOOK_SECRET');",
              "if (!secret) return;",
              "const raw = pm.request.body && pm.request.body.raw;",
              "if (!raw) return;",
              "const sig = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(raw, secret).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
              "pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-signature', value: sig });"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST order_updated",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"order_updated\": {\n    \"orderId\": \"tu-etherfuse-order-id\",\n    \"status\": \"completed\",\n    \"confirmedTxSignature\": \"abc123\"\n  }\n}\n"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/webhooks/etherfuse"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST kyc_updated",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"kyc_updated\": {\n    \"customerId\": \"tu-customer-id\",\n    \"approved\": true,\n    \"updateReason\": \"\"\n  }\n}\n"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/webhooks/etherfuse"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "POST bank_account_updated",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bank_account_updated\": {\n    \"bankAccountId\": \"tu-bank-account-id\",\n    \"status\": \"active\"\n  }\n}\n"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/webhooks/etherfuse"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
